=head1 NAME

SOURCE_PAIRS_ON_SLIT - Reduce point source observations.

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This recipe is obsolete now. You should probably be using the new
POINT_SOURCE recipe. We keep this recipe availiable simply for old
data. This recipe is functionally identical to POINT_SOURCE.

See the POINT_SOURCE recipe documentation for details.

